"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Preventive measures for acute diarrhea among children in developing settings include breastfeeding, consumption of safe food and water, adherence to hygienic practices and vaccination against rotavirus infection. (See",
"      <a class=\"local\" href=\"#H1159942574\">",
"       'Prevention'",
"      </a>",
"      above.)",
"     </li>",
